      "iteration": "single",
      "description": "敷地境界線のうち有効道路に接する部分の長さを算出する",
      "logicExpression": "L = length(intersection(敷地境界, R))",
      "relatedArticles": ["法::A43:P1"],
      "softwareFunctions": [
        {
          "category": "program_processing",
          "description": "幾何学的演算による長さ算出"
        }
